 <title> Состојбата на електронските услуги во РМ 2017</title>
 <link>http://novica.discindo.org/mk/node/861</link>
 <description>&lt;section class=&quot;field field-name-taxonomy-vocabulary-1 field-type-taxonomy-term-reference field-label-above view-mode-rss&quot;&gt;&lt;h2 class=&quot;field-label&quot;&gt;Tags:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/5&quot;&gt;македонија&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/9&quot;&gt;слободен софтвер&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/141&quot;&gt;отворени податоци&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item odd&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/44&quot;&gt;отворени стандарди&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/mk/taxonomy/term/43&quot;&gt;авторски права&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden view-mode-rss&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Ова требаше да биде блог-пост, но заради полесно ажурирање продолжува на &lt;a href=&quot;https://wiki.spodeli.org/VendorLockInMakedonija&quot;&gt;вики&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
